description: House dom Christian Wilde and Van receive a shipment of boys today. Paul Wagner and Derrick Hanson are tied up and blindfolded. They are ready to be processed. The house doms determine which are future doms or subs and which will be returned to the streets. Paul has an easy demeanor and makes a great sub. On the other hand, Derrick has a certain air about him so Van puts him through the wringer to test his toughness.
title: Meat Processing
